  31:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) Declare a SRAM_HandleTypeDef handle structure, for example:
  32:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****           SRAM_HandleTypeDef  hsram; and:
  33:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  34:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (++) Fill the SRAM_HandleTypeDef handle "Init" field with the allowed
  35:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             values of the structure member.
  36:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  37:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (++) Fill the SRAM_HandleTypeDef handle "Instance" field with a predefined
  38:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             base register instance for NOR or SRAM device
  39:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  40:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (++) Fill the SRAM_HandleTypeDef handle "Extended" field with a predefined
  41:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             base register instance for NOR or SRAM extended mode
  42:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  43:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) Declare two FMC_NORSRAM_TimingTypeDef structures, for both normal and extended
  44:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        mode timings; for example:
  45:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****           FMC_NORSRAM_TimingTypeDef  Timing and FMC_NORSRAM_TimingTypeDef  ExTiming;
  46:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       and fill its fields with the allowed values of the structure member.
  47:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  48:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) Initialize the SRAM Controller by calling the function HAL_SRAM_Init(). This function
  49:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        performs the following sequence:
  50:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  51:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (##) MSP hardware layer configuration using the function HAL_SRAM_MspInit()
  52:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (##) Control register configuration using the FMC NORSRAM interface function
  53:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             FMC_NORSRAM_Init()
  54:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (##) Timing register configuration using the FMC NORSRAM interface function
  55:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             FMC_NORSRAM_Timing_Init()
  56:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (##) Extended mode Timing register configuration using the FMC NORSRAM interface function
  57:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****             FMC_NORSRAM_Extended_Timing_Init()
  58:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (##) Enable the SRAM device using the macro __FMC_NORSRAM_ENABLE()
  59:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  60:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) At this stage you can perform read/write accesses from/to the memory connected
  61:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        to the NOR/SRAM Bank. You can perform either polling or DMA transfer using the
  62:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        following APIs:
  63:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (++) HAL_SRAM_Read()/HAL_SRAM_Write() for polling read/write access
  64:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        (++) HAL_SRAM_Read_DMA()/HAL_SRAM_Write_DMA() for DMA read/write transfer
  65:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  66:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) You can also control the SRAM device by calling the control APIs HAL_SRAM_WriteOperation_Ena
  67:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        HAL_SRAM_WriteOperation_Disable() to respectively enable/disable the SRAM write operation
  68:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  69:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****    (#) You can continuously monitor the SRAM device HAL state by calling the function
  70:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        HAL_SRAM_GetState()
  71:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  72:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****        *** Callback registration ***
  73:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****     =============================================
  74:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****     [..]
  75:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       The compilation define  USE_HAL_SRAM_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
  76:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
  77:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  78:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       Use Functions HAL_SRAM_RegisterCallback() to register a user callback,
  79:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       it allows to register following callbacks:
  80:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****         (+) MspInitCallback    : SRAM MspInit.
  81:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****         (+) MspDeInitCallback  : SRAM MspDeInit.
  82:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
  83:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       and a pointer to the user callback function.
  84:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c **** 
  85:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       Use function HAL_SRAM_UnRegisterCallback() to reset a callback to the default
  86:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****       weak (overridden) function. It allows to reset following callbacks:
  87:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_sram.c ****         (+) MspInitCallback    : SRAM MspInit.
